CoinMKT is a US-based [[currency_exchange]] which supports USD for trading between Bitcoins and other cryptocurrencies, including [[Litecoin]], [[PPCoin]], TerraCoin, NovaCoins, and [[Namecoin]].

CoinMKT is currently in public beta with real money trading, visit http://coinmkt.com

##Features

###Cross Platform
CoinMKT's HTML5 web app can be used on any device with any screen size.

###Cold Storage
CoinMKT keeps 90% of deposits in cold storage (offline) to prevent mass theft.

###Trade Any Currency Pair
CoinMKT allows the inter-trading of any currency pair from the currencies it supports.

###Currency pairs

* BTC => / USD / LTC / PPC / TRC / NVC / NMC / FTC
* LTC => / USD / BTC / PPC / TRC / NVC / NMC / FTC
* PPC => / USD / BTC / LTC / TRC / NVC / NMC / FTC
* TRC => / USD / BTC / LTC / PPC / NVC / NMC / FTC
* NVC => / USD / BTC / LTC / PPC / TRC / NMC / FTC
* NMC => / USD / BTC / LTC / PPC / TRC / NVC / FTC
* FTC => / USD / BTC / LTC / PPC / TRC / NVC / NMC


###Deposit Options

####Cryptocurrencies
CoinMKT does not charge a deposit fee for any supported [[Digital_currency]] including Bitcoins, Litecoins, PPCoins, TerraCoins, NovaCoins, NameCoins, or FeatherCoins

####USD

* [[Dwolla]]
* Bank Account (ACH / eCheck)
* International Wire Transfer
* Money Order

####EUR
(coming soon)

* SEPA bank transfer (fee applies)


